#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cauthentication-iam.md:114
msgid ""
"Attribute mapping: BSN, KvK number, Level of Assurance (LoA), eIDAS "
"assurance level"
msgstr ""

